# L-shaped prism: 2x2x1 footprint with 1x1x1 notch cut from upper-right
# Cross-section (xz-plane): corners at (0,0),(2,0),(2,1),(1,1),(1,2),(0,2)
# Extruded from y=0 to y=1
# 12 vertices, 20 triangular faces

v 0 0 0
v 2 0 0
v 2 0 1
v 1 0 1
v 1 0 2
v 0 0 2
v 0 1 0
v 2 1 0
v 2 1 1
v 1 1 1
v 1 1 2
v 0 1 2

# front face (y=0), normal -y
f 1 2 3
f 1 3 4
f 1 4 5
f 1 5 6

# back face (y=1), normal +y
f 7 12 11
f 7 11 10
f 7 10 9
f 7 9 8

# bottom (z=0), normal -z
f 1 7 8
f 1 8 2

# right (x=2), normal +x
f 2 8 9
f 2 9 3

# inner horizontal step (z=1, x=1..2), normal +z
f 3 9 10
f 3 10 4

# inner vertical step (x=1, z=1..2), normal +x
f 4 10 11
f 4 11 5

# top (z=2), normal +z
f 5 11 12
f 5 12 6

# left (x=0), normal -x
f 6 12 7
f 6 7 1
